#786387=IFCCLASSIFICATION('NBS','July 2017','2017-07-01','NBS Create','The UK Government Construction Strategy published May 2011 require collaborative 3D building information modelling (BIM). This requirement was defined as Level 2 BIM. NBS Create can be used as a key collaboration tool within a Level 2 BIM project. NBS Create can be linked to your design tool and the National BIM library to enable information to flow throughout a project resulting in coordinated, accurate design documentation produced efficiently and maximizing the benefits of BIM.','http://www.nationalbimlibrary.com/API/Classification.aspx',('_','/'));
#786388=IFCRELASSOCIATESCLASSIFICATION('1KjA867Db8Lgs4Rs1OQgmO',$,$,$,(#1),#786387);
#786401=IFCCLASSIFICATION('RICS','1','2017-03-20','RICS NRM3','NRM 3 gives guidance on the quantification and description of maintenance works for the purpose of preparing initial order of cost estimates. The rules also aid the procurement and cost control of maintenance works. Assigns category classification to building elements based on RICS''s New Rules of Measurement. It defines the order of cost estimating and elemental cost planning for building maintenance works.','http://www.rics.org',('.'));
